# The Member Wins™

**Full document:** `docs/THE_MEMBER_WINS.md`

## The question (every design decision)

> **Does this make life easier for the member?**

No or unclear → redesign. Do not implement.

## Precedence

**Member ease wins** over implementation convenience · coding simplicity · traditional software design · dev velocity · technical elegance.

## With frozen architecture

Specs change only when [repeated testing](../docs/SPARK_CONVERSATION_ARCHITECTURE_FREEZE.md) proves measurably better member experience — not because change is easier to build.

Future ideas → [Parking Lot](../docs/PARKING_LOT.md) until milestone complete.

**Principle:** [The Member Wins™](../docs/THE_MEMBER_WINS.md)
